reviewText: I ordered "The Best of James" for a Santa gift, but received "The Best of Thomas" instead.  My husband was home when the package arrived, opened it and tossed the packaging.  By the time I found out about the video (days later), I had no access to an address to return it to.  He tells me that there was no packaging slip in the envelope.  Not sure what really happened, other than the fact that the wrong video was sent, and I am stuck with it.
